      "date": "2018-04-17 08:23:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nI tested this patch on a TCP routed LNet network. It improves the situation, as communication between nodes beyond the router does not stop working right after the timeout. But strangely, it does not work steadily. I get intermittent failures when doing 'lctl ping', and it seems to get worse as time goes by.",
